Definition: money in the form of cash that is readily available
Example: his wife was always a good source of ready cash; he paid cold cash for the TV set
Synonyms: cold_cash, ready_money, cash, money, in, the, form, of, that, is, readily, available, his, wife, was, always, a, good, source, ready, he, paid, cold, for, TV, set
Category: noun.possession
